DataElement.preferredDefinition: Someone who gives blood or tissue or an organ to be used in another person._One of the 12 divisions of a year as determined by a calendar.  It corresponds to the unit of time of approximately to one cycle of the moon's phases, about 30 days or 4 weeks.:Continuance of life or existence especially under adverse conditions; includes methods and philosophy of survival.:How much there is of something that you can measure; the total amount or number._Generic value domain for a primitive java dataype that is an Integer (32-bit two's complement).
